title: Husband is Bored in Marriage After Baby is Born
itunes:title: Husband is Bored in Marriage After Baby is Born
description: Join Megan Wyatt as she answers Wives of Jannah community member marriage related questions from her inbox. This episode addresses a wife whose husband feels consistently bored especially since the birth of their daughter who came within the first year of their marriage.
